{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightLightnessLinearSet"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightLightnessLinearSet\/continueTransaction","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","extendedModule":"NordicMesh","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh18TransactionMessagePAAE08continueC0Sbvp::SYNTHESIZED::s:10NordicMesh23LightLightnessLinearSetV","title":"continueTransaction","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The messages within a transaction carry the cumulative values of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a field. In case one or more messages within a transaction are not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"received by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"carrying cumulative values of the field.","type":"text"}]},{"type":